{
  "page": "Ulf",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">This article is about the Vale clansman. For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Ulf_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Ulf (disambiguation)\">Ulf (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brothers\" title=\"Moon Brothers\"><img alt=\"Moon Brothers.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/50px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/75px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/100px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Ulf<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> son of Umar</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brothers\" title=\"Moon Brothers\"><img alt=\"Moon Brothers.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/50px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/75px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/100px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:UlfSonofUmar_by_Daarken.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"UlfSonofUmar by Daarken.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3c/UlfSonofUmar_by_Daarken.jpg/350px-UlfSonofUmar_by_Daarken.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"263\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3c/UlfSonofUmar_by_Daarken.jpg/525px-UlfSonofUmar_by_Daarken.jpg 1.5x, /images/3/3c/UlfSonofUmar_by_Daarken.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Ulf by Daarken © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brothers\" title=\"Moon Brothers\">Moon Brothers</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">Vale mountain clans</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_on_the_Green_Fork\" title=\"Battle on the Green Fork\">Green Fork</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Umar\" title=\"Umar\">Umar</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Ulf</b>, known as <b>Ulf son of Umar</b> after <a href=\"/index.php/Umar\" title=\"Umar\">his father</a>, is a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brothers\" title=\"Moon Brothers\">Moon Brothers</a>, one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">Vale mountain clans</a> found in the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Mountains of the Moon\">Mountains of the Moon</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ulf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ulf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ulf is the leader of the <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brothers\" title=\"Moon Brothers\">Moon Brothers</a> who accompany <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> to his father <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>'s encampment on the promise of weapons and armor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Lefford\" title=\"Leo Lefford\">Leo Lefford</a> is displeased when Tyrion requests arms and armor from him for Ulf's men.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ulf demands blood money when three <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\">Stone Crows</a> kill a Moon Brother, but <a href=\"/index.php/Conn\" title=\"Conn\">Conn</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Shagga\" title=\"Shagga\">Shagga</a> refuse to pay.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ulf is slain during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_on_the_Green_Fork\" title=\"Battle on the Green Fork\">battle on the Green Fork</a>. After the battle, Tyrion finds Ulf with his arm gone at the elbow and a dozen Moon Brothers dead around him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ulf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Tywin</b>: Ride with me against my enemies, and you shall have all <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">my son</a> promised you, and more.<br />\n</p><p><b>Ulf</b>: Would you pay us with our own coin? Why should we need the father's promise, when we have the son's?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Tywin</b>: I said nothing of need. My words were courtesy, nothing more. You need not join us. The <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">men of the winterlands</a> are made of iron and ice, and even my boldest <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> fear to face them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> and Ulf</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ulf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 56\">Chapter 56</a>, Tyrion VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_62\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 62\">Chapter 62</a>, Tyrion V